{"tid":1488682,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑藍絲男朋友出軌，佢follow咗大波madam後成個人唔同晒","createTime":"2019-08-19T16:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T02:51:29.000Z","uid":179648,"like":348,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"62937abdd3e2cfed85c15c5f6be804fbccc33e6d","tid":1488682,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:28:15.000Z","msg":"我男朋友本身好乖，係愛國愛港愛我嘅藍絲，最近佢好奇怪，成日weekend唔陪我，夜一夜先返屋企。<br />\n<br />\n我發現佢ig成日睇一個大波妹，叫Katy Pang，一定係比佢帶壞，成日出去示威！我查咗好耐，原來Katy Pang係警察部做緊臥底，佢深黃架！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">各位港女，我懷疑呢個深黃madam有好多姦夫，呢個時候香港好需要你</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">幫港捉姦，光復香港。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我＃1男朋友Ernest<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hL0RuVv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhL0RuVv.jpg&h=82e1b141&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eS2MiOS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeS2MiOS.jpg&h=fb3ee519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pddSYOR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpddSYOR.jpg&h=e8bacee8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我＃2男朋友Jimmy<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zc1xenR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzc1xenR.jpg&h=a1dec3f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VC0h9Wc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVC0h9Wc.jpg&h=a8bfaafa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我＃3男朋友吳家浩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdbJk3m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdbJk3m.jpg&h=ee93abe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0SaBF3k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0SaBF3k.jpg&h=7e621c87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有幾十個男朋友，得閒先貼。<br />\n<br />\n我今日見到個follow人數直線上升，再諗一諗中槍受傷被捕嘅義士，真係嬲到仆街。即刻上ig瘋狂back up follow佢嘅仆街。<br />\n<br />\n大陸人，澳門人，香港藍絲我算，黃絲我都算，但你班仆街有份上街，有女朋友，你有咩資格！？屌你老母。"},{"pid":"134a24ae9ab00a7a9d9c04f01b96163a624fe5f0","tid":1488682,"uid":179648,"like":58,"dislike":3,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:31:47.000Z","msg":"我忍撚咗半日，下就back up完一轉，夜晚對多次，見到手頭上有資料嘅人有unfollow返我就算數，當你貪玩。<br />\n<br />\n但上面貼出嚟嘅follow咗大半日都未unfollow，我而家未貼晒你大頭同女朋友已經手下留情。"},{"pid":"2c4f3cc4dd95b6b9cd338502d66c10995778d5e3","tid":1488682,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:31:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"862e838156873466f259ac60cf7e8ef178e93874","tid":1488682,"uid":179648,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:33:10.000Z","msg":"你班男朋友好彩，黃絲madam private咗我無得繼續捉你，但手頭上尾經有大把姦夫資料！"},{"pid":"dda6cff86c56e171fafb9fb0ffa2815f1caeee78","tid":1488682,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:33:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16f698b3a41ea9c453de2740d0ab1a623798609e","tid":1488682,"uid":140094,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:33:58.000Z","msg":"做得好<br />\n你班人咪精蟲上腦啦屌你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbce9ba56ac3fb73445b93e71a8eb257a9372284","tid":1488682,"uid":179648,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"16f698b3a41ea9c453de2740d0ab1a623798609e","tid":1488682,"uid":140094,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:33:58.000Z","msg":"做得好<br />\n你班人咪精蟲上腦啦屌你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:36:05.000Z","msg":"多謝，幫手推下<br />\n唔鞭下呢班男朋友點堅定返軍心！"},{"pid":"186f35be86c773208caf5d20cc6ecf07fad167f2","tid":1488682,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl