3m.jpg&h=ee93abe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0SaBF3k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0SaBF3k.jpg&h=7e621c87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有幾十個男朋友，得閒先貼。<br />\n<br />\n我今日見到個follow人數直線上升，再諗一諗中槍受傷被捕嘅義士，真係嬲到仆街。即刻上ig瘋狂back up follow佢嘅仆街。<br />\n<br />\n大陸人，澳門人，香港藍絲我算，黃絲我都算，但你班仆街有份上街，有女朋友，你有咩資格！？屌你老母。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:02:50.000Z","msg":"樓主不如逐個屌醒他們啦。"},{"pid":"01f98f2fd9afd730990a5a0ade9c06280aec5db1","tid":1488682,"uid":179648,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7f660db90554a23b8ffb78968f4d54d2459179d1","tid":1488682,"uid":8880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:02:42.000Z","msg":"支持 呢班柒頭真係傻撚咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:04:13.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲好嬲<br />\n我己經等咗大半日先出手<br />\n比機會佢地Unfollow"},{"pid":"cd9db495491516303b1869ddef12bb136c9d52b2","tid":1488682,"uid":29126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:05:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88ced6a1e1b23ba1b9096a7964e3986cd05dde13","tid":1488682,"uid":179648,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:06:05.000Z","msg":"大陸人藍絲follow你你唔會嬲<br />\n但見到呢啲有時會打下卡，貼下文宣嘅黃絲follow madam，係嬲到仆街<br />\n<br />\n人地幫你擋子彈，你係冷氣房打J"},{"pid":"6589b818fa221ba685f9e1c130478f6c65a22ab9","tid":1488682,"uid":179648,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:06:46.000Z","msg":"大陸人同藍絲follow你係唔會嬲<br />\n但見到呢啲有時會打下卡，貼下文宣嘅黃絲follow madam，係嬲到仆街<br />\n<br />\n人地幫你擋子彈，你係冷氣房打J"},{"pid":"769fb0420b1e4dbc1d21bf20b154d7f4646e6734","tid":1488682,"uid":179648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:08:23.000Z","msg":"大陸人同藍絲follow你係唔會嬲<br />\n但見到呢啲有時會打下卡，貼下文宣嘅黃絲follow madam，係嬲到仆街<br />\n<br />\n人地幫你擋子彈，你係冷氣房打J"},{"pid":"bdcf066334ede3717fc3d11c4b6a6c71eb54ed58","tid":1488682,"uid":308961,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:08:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be07004